\f0\b\fs48 \cf0 Set default parameter\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri1060\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 \

\f0 Before you install Dr.seq, we suggest you to set default parameter (including the path of your annotation file, mapping index and path of major software.) To set default parameter:\
\pard\pardeftab720\li720\fi-360\ri1060\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 1.	Find the template of configure file under \'93lib/Config/\'94 of this package\
2.	Set default parameter in the template configure file (PLEASE don\'92t change the name of template file and change or delete the name of any parameter)\
3.	Save your change and install Dr.seq. Dr.seq generate configure files according to this template, so the parameter you set will shown on the new configure file Dr.seq generate next time. \
\pard\pardeftab720\ri1060\partightenfactor0

